messages.content: Seriya is back in his house! He is washing up and has changed into normal wear! Hes just sitting on his couch now.
Seriya is just now making caramel over the stove. Theres already pre popped popcorn in a bowl. Easy peasy caramel popcorn.
Seriya has packed a bag full of caramel popcorn and little chocolates.   Fun!
Argenti knock knock knockin on the door

Theres a small sound of clicking and crashing before seriya opens the door. Hes in his normal attire but hes holding a Bouquet of flowers. He waves hello with his free hand. “Hello Argenti! I didnt expect you to be here so soon!”
"Are you ok?"
“Yep, Im good! Ahah...You should come in.” Seriya holds open the door for him as he still holds the Bouquet. This didnt go as planned, but He can work with it.
//watch Argenti be oblivious.
"I heard a lot of crashing...but if you insist!" He walks in
Seriya just nods as he takes Argenti to sit with him on the couch. It takes a while for him speak up about anything, But he does look over to Argenti. “Hm..I wanted..to tell you something Argenti.”
"Yes?"
“I like you alot! Romantically speaking, i mean.” Seriya just looks down as he shoves the flowers to Argenti. Seriya honestly looks like hes about to just completely bail.
"Oh wow..." Argenti's face reddened. "That's.... such a relief. I've thought about you that way for a long time!" He accepts the flowers and gives Seriya a big ol hug
“Wait really? Have we just been chasing circles around eachother?” Seriya just hugs him back. He slowly lays down on the couch to make it more comfortable for Argenti.
"Maybe!"
“Should we just lay here? I bet the others will want to hear this later.” Seriya chuckles a bit as he pats Argenti on the back.
"I suppose..." He smiles. He was very content with just laying here.
“Ah, Okay.” Seriya gives him a kiss on the forehead before just laying back down. He is very happy with how this went, aswell as now them laying together.
Argenti has a brain fart and forgets how to romance so he just...boops Seriya's nose
Seriya smiles as he does the same to Argenti. After that he just lays there for a while with him until he falls asleep. He has a tight grip when hes sleeping.
Argenti falls asleep eventually too, tho it takes him a long time. He's just happy to be in this moment.
Seriya is just having an awful feeling rn. He doesnt know what it is, but its absolutely terrifying. His gut is telling him to run back to Polaris’ house but his brain doesnt wanna die.

Seriya carries Argenti back to his house as he plops him down onto the couch. He goes around his house putting blankets and Pillows on him to make him more comfy. Seriya flicks Argenti’s forehead a few times. “Hey. Hey Argenti. Are you alive?”

"Well, it'll happen regardless of my contribution...and I want to be able to keep my friends safe...."
Seriya has no idea whats happening, but he gets up from his chair and sits next to argenti. Patting him on the back.
"Good morning, Seriya!"
“Good morning. Is everything alright with you? Something seems wrong. How are you?”
"Oh, Shale is plotting a rebellion against the plasma."
Seriya is just. Not processing this. He lays down for a few minutes.
"Seriya?"
“Sorry. Im just shocked. I might just lay here for a while.” Seriya grumbles a bit as he stares at his ceiling.
"I'm joining it. Then I'm gonna lay down with you."
“Ah. Alright. Should i come along with you?” Seriya had just been thinking about this. This would change everything. For good or bad.
"Well...I don't want you getting hurt...."
“I dont want you getting hurt either. But i cant stop you from joining. So ill just have to go with you.” Seriya gives Argenti a pat on the back.
"Know if there's a projectile coming your way, IM going to know YOU out of the way!"
“That wont happen. Promise.” Seriya sighs as her looked to argenti. Going on his phone.
"don't try to save my ass this time."
“You know i will if you get into trouble. I do care for you alot.”
"Remember when Abdul said 'if you get lost or injured I won't come to your rescue'? Whatever happened to that?"
“Well, I wont come get you if you get lost but you are kinda my boyfriend now. I wanna look after you.”
"Don't sacrifice your life for me."
“I wont. Haven’t i told you this already? Im not gonna die for you, but i’ll try and at least help you. Thats all i could do really.”
Argenti was silent before hugging his bf
Seriya was just alittle shocked at the sudden hug, but he softened a bit as he hugged Argenti back. Patting him on the back.
Argenti was happy

"I'm back."
“Argenti! What the hell! I cant believe you would run out like that. You have to rest.”
"It's fine. All I did was meet some neighbors of ours."
“Thats good but, seriously you worried me.” Seriya pinched the bridge of his nose as he just looked at Argenti.
"I think everyone survived."
“Argenti what does that mean. Your phrasing concerns me.”
"There was apparently a battle against the plasma today."
“Ah i see. Im glad everyone survived but are you hurt anywhere? Other than when Malachite beat you up.”
"Nah. I'm fine. Kinda wanna go back to my house and get some stuff."

"It played the sounds of...Diavolo killing Polnareff."
“I apologize, but im not familiar with Diavolo. But it concerns me that it was playing audio from when he killed Polnareff. Im gonna hope it doesnt play audio clips of the present.”
"Luckily it seems this camera in my house was mysteriously turned on...also a lot of my soup cans were empty."
Argenti played the footage
It was mundane until a broken Jouta doll suddenly appeared on his living room floor
“Soup cans? Odd.” Seriya just watched with no concern of the footage until he saw the doll appear. “Ah. So thats what you meant. Its concerning that it just came out of no where to your house.”
"I'm better now."
“Hm. Im getting an awful sense of dread..probably nothing i hope.” Seriya just goes back to reading his book.
